WEBVTT

01:40.520 --> 01:41.360
He!

01:51.040 --> 01:52.160
He!

01:52.680 --> 01:53.800
He!

02:00.080 --> 02:01.160
He!

02:05.040 --> 02:06.200
He!

02:06.880 --> 02:10.639
In 2002, my dad
had a stroke for the first time,

02:11.520 --> 02:13.320
and he fell into the rooftop shaft.

02:14.000 --> 02:14.960
And then,

02:15.920 --> 02:18.720
he was heavily injured in an operation.

02:20.280 --> 02:21.520
And later,

02:22.840 --> 02:27.160
the sudden passing of his apprentice
exacerbated his condition.

02:27.240 --> 02:28.880
Two years ago, he went into retirement.

02:28.960 --> 02:30.760
Out of nowhere, he received
something left behind by his apprentice.

02:31.440 --> 02:33.000
Perhaps it triggered something in him.

02:33.080 --> 02:35.840
His condition acted up, and he fainted.

02:36.480 --> 02:38.440
In his mind, his apprentice never died.

02:38.520 --> 02:41.200
He merely went to Beijing
to teach for 12 years.

02:41.720 --> 02:43.720
Whenever his apprentice appeared,

02:43.800 --> 02:46.640
he'd convince him to stay
to help him investigate cases.

02:47.360 --> 02:51.000
It seems like his memory is stuck in 2002.

03:18.000 --> 03:19.760
I waited for you for five years!

03:20.840 --> 03:22.000
Why didn't you save me?

03:22.080 --> 03:23.360
Why?

03:24.160 --> 03:25.560
Come back.

03:26.160 --> 03:28.120
I'm waiting for you. Come down.

03:28.200 --> 03:30.600
Keep me company. You…

04:02.120 --> 04:03.160
Doctor.

04:03.240 --> 04:04.680
Doctor!

04:06.280 --> 04:08.120
He. You're awake.

04:08.720 --> 04:10.160
Why am I here?

04:14.800 --> 04:16.839
You fell into the rooftop shaft yesterday.

04:16.920 --> 04:19.519
Fortunately, no bone fractures.
Just some cuts.

04:19.600 --> 04:20.800
Fortunately?

04:20.880 --> 04:22.079
Officer He,

04:22.160 --> 04:25.080
you fell because you had a stroke,
and you lost consciousness.

04:25.160 --> 04:26.240
I checked your medical records.

04:26.320 --> 04:28.040
Your cholesterol, blood sugar,
and blood pressure levels

04:28.120 --> 04:29.240
are dangerously high.

04:29.320 --> 04:30.680
Did you take medication regularly?

04:31.280 --> 04:33.800
Taking pills during all three of my meals?

04:33.880 --> 04:35.120
Who can live like that?

04:35.200 --> 04:36.120
Listen.

04:36.200 --> 04:38.360
Your condition is serious.
You have to take your medication.

04:38.440 --> 04:40.600
Otherwise, this will happen again,

04:40.680 --> 04:42.680
-and it will be more serious.
-Okay.

04:43.640 --> 04:45.040
There are no other huge issues,

04:45.120 --> 04:46.880
but you will stay here for a few days.

04:46.960 --> 04:48.160
Thanks, Doctor.

05:02.560 --> 05:03.400
Captain Feng just left.

05:04.720 --> 05:06.000
He told me everything.

05:07.240 --> 05:10.720
Are you intending
to take full responsibility?

05:11.840 --> 05:14.840
Did you tell Captain Feng
that you want to go to Beijing to teach?

05:25.520 --> 05:26.440
He.

05:29.520 --> 05:32.600
I'd like to apologize to you.
It's my fault.

05:33.280 --> 05:36.080
Whether it's the missing persons case
or the homicide,

05:36.160 --> 05:39.600
I shouldn't have brought
my emotions into the case.

05:48.720 --> 05:49.760
Give me your hand.

05:51.000 --> 05:53.000
-That hand.
-Why?

05:53.960 --> 05:54.800
Press this.

05:57.520 --> 05:59.080
He, what are you doing?
What about your IV drip?

05:59.160 --> 06:01.040
Now is not the time to lie down.

06:01.800 --> 06:02.920
Let's go. We have a case to crack.

06:06.320 --> 06:07.160
Come.

06:13.840 --> 06:14.720
In the June 30th case,

06:14.800 --> 06:17.520
Song Qingsong is undeniably
the main suspect.

06:17.600 --> 06:21.200
But he allegedly fled
to the US five years ago.

06:22.440 --> 06:23.840
Immigrating is suspicious enough.

06:23.920 --> 06:26.200
Back then, Song Qingsong
hired someone to commit a murder.

06:26.280 --> 06:29.120
But he was acquitted
due to a lack of evidence.

06:29.200 --> 06:31.120
We could only charge him with bribery.

06:31.200 --> 06:32.960
Even then, it wasn't that serious.

06:33.040 --> 06:34.920
He would get five years in jail at most.

06:35.000 --> 06:37.080
And when he would be released,
he would still be the same old him.

06:37.160 --> 06:40.080
The factory, the car,
and the property would still be his.

06:40.680 --> 06:41.680
So why did he flee?

06:41.760 --> 06:43.480
I did investigate him.

06:43.560 --> 06:45.520
Song Qingsong had dealings in both
legitimate and illegitimate channels.

06:45.600 --> 06:47.680
He's definitely not a good person,

06:47.760 --> 06:49.600
but he's kind to his factory workers.

06:49.680 --> 06:51.360
Those workers have worked
for him for more than a decade.

06:51.440 --> 06:55.000
Oh. He also has a son
who was only three years old when he fled.

06:56.160 --> 07:00.360
So there's probably another story
behind his hiring of the hitman.

07:00.440 --> 07:02.480
The most effective way

07:02.560 --> 07:04.720
to investigate Song Qingsong
is through Wu Shanlong.

07:04.800 --> 07:07.640
But after he took over the cement factory,
he accrued debts

07:07.720 --> 07:09.120
and is now in hiding.

07:10.640 --> 07:11.880
Turn right at the intersection in front.

07:13.120 --> 07:14.160
We're not returning to the station?

07:14.240 --> 07:16.000
Shouldn't we find Wu Shanlong?

07:22.880 --> 07:25.920
HONGYUN HUIHUANG CLUB

07:39.400 --> 07:40.520
Who are you?

07:40.600 --> 07:42.320
This is the dressing room.

07:45.120 --> 07:47.920
Are you new here?

07:50.520 --> 07:52.600
I'm Wu. W-U.

07:53.320 --> 07:54.640
Shanlong is my name.

07:55.240 --> 07:58.760
I am the biggest shareholder of this club.

07:58.840 --> 08:00.920
Qingsong Cement Factory. Ever heard of it?

08:01.000 --> 08:02.280
It's mine too.

08:04.320 --> 08:07.120
Perhaps I could book all of you today,

08:07.840 --> 08:10.840
so that you can get some good rest.

08:12.000 --> 08:13.040
Hi, Mei.

08:13.720 --> 08:15.080
-Hi, Mei.
-Hi, Mei.

08:15.160 --> 08:16.720
Hi.

08:21.160 --> 08:22.520
Come out here.

08:38.559 --> 08:40.720
Leeching off this place every day.

08:42.240 --> 08:44.000
Do I owe you anything or what?

08:49.200 --> 08:51.000
Did I hear that correctly?

08:51.080 --> 08:53.280
Do you even know who you're talking to?

08:54.040 --> 08:55.040
Wu Shanlong.

08:55.720 --> 08:57.360
From now on,

08:57.440 --> 08:59.520
I won't lend a single cent to you.

09:02.760 --> 09:05.280
Zhao Hongmei. I see you've grown arrogant.

09:05.360 --> 09:06.760
Without me,

09:06.840 --> 09:08.920
you would still have been the owner
of that small massage parlor.

09:09.000 --> 09:10.600
Who gave you your first fortune?

09:10.680 --> 09:12.240
It was me, Wu Shanlong. It was me.

09:12.320 --> 09:14.280
Without me, this place would still
be called Dahuihuang.

09:18.760 --> 09:20.000
You helped me?

09:20.080 --> 09:21.680
Do you even have the wits for it?

09:21.760 --> 09:23.120
Without me,

09:23.200 --> 09:25.080
Song Qingsong would still
be running the cement factory,

09:25.600 --> 09:28.120
-and you would still be his chauffeur.
-What did you say?

09:28.200 --> 09:30.160
-I gave you your share of the money.
-Say that again.

09:30.240 --> 09:32.480
I gave you your share of the money.
You are just incompetent.

09:32.560 --> 09:35.120
The cement factory was a gold mine,
but you messed it up.

09:35.920 --> 09:38.480
And now, you're leeching off me.

09:38.560 --> 09:41.240
I've treated you with enough generosity.

09:41.960 --> 09:43.320
Am I the shareholder here or not?

09:43.400 --> 09:45.240
I can come and go whenever I want.

09:45.320 --> 09:47.960
Of course. Come whenever you want.

09:49.080 --> 09:50.920
But before you come,

09:51.440 --> 09:53.680
clean up the mess you made.

09:53.760 --> 09:55.200
What mess?

09:55.280 --> 09:57.000
Tell me. What mess?

09:57.080 --> 09:58.640
Still playing dumb?

09:59.560 --> 10:01.040
The police just released a statement.

10:01.120 --> 10:03.960
Xu Zhihong's body was found in Yuanlongli.

10:04.040 --> 10:05.600
They are investigating it everywhere now.

10:09.560 --> 10:10.800
You killed Xu Meng too.

10:11.480 --> 10:14.120
You are now a murderer.

10:14.200 --> 10:15.920
Why don't you learn
from your brother-in-law?

10:16.000 --> 10:18.840
Just run away. Run.

10:18.920 --> 10:21.560
When you're gone, everyone will be safe.

10:22.240 --> 10:24.000
The girls under me?

10:24.840 --> 10:27.640
I can't guarantee
they are as loyal as I am.

10:27.720 --> 10:29.600
If one of them gets drunk
and runs their mouth,

10:29.680 --> 10:31.000
I won't be able to stop them.

10:31.960 --> 10:32.800
Sure.

10:35.000 --> 10:35.960
I can run away.

10:36.040 --> 10:38.120
But I need you to give me some money.

10:38.200 --> 10:39.760
Are you crazy?

10:51.160 --> 10:52.000
Zhao Hongmei.

10:53.920 --> 10:56.120
You're talking to a murderer now.

10:57.280 --> 10:59.800
How many lives do you risk by defying me?

11:05.560 --> 11:06.680
Defying you? What about that?

11:06.760 --> 11:08.920
What about that?
I won't comply, so kill me now.

11:10.640 --> 11:12.920
Do you want to see
if I will go to the police right now?

11:13.000 --> 11:14.440
Please be patient, sir.

11:14.520 --> 11:16.120
Our manager is having a meeting. You…

11:20.960 --> 11:23.240
What a coincidence.
My two old friends are here.

11:23.320 --> 11:25.160
Great. Let's hang out.

11:27.120 --> 11:29.480
Officer He. Officer Ran. You're here.

11:29.560 --> 11:32.760
I was just reminiscing
about the past with Mr. Wu here.

11:32.840 --> 11:33.920
We talked about you two.

11:34.000 --> 11:36.880
-Speak of the devil, really.
-Is that so?

11:37.920 --> 11:39.040
-Zhang!
-Yes?

11:39.120 --> 11:40.920
How is the speaker outside going?

11:41.000 --> 11:43.320
-It's almost done, Mei.
-Show me.

11:44.000 --> 11:46.360
I have work to do. Mr. Hu,

11:46.440 --> 11:48.920
entertain our old friends here, will you?

11:49.000 --> 11:50.040
I'll count on you. Take a seat.

11:50.120 --> 11:51.800
Order anything you want. Take a seat.

11:52.560 --> 11:53.800
Take a seat.

11:53.880 --> 11:54.840
Officer Ran!

11:55.440 --> 11:56.840
You're more handsome than before.

12:10.880 --> 12:12.000
Speak.

12:12.080 --> 12:14.360
Tell us about Xu Meng and her father.

12:16.040 --> 12:17.720
What are you on about, Officer He?

12:18.400 --> 12:19.480
I don't know them.

12:23.120 --> 12:24.640
Wu Shanlong,

12:24.720 --> 12:27.280
between us, there's no need to play coy.

12:31.640 --> 12:34.360
Back then, Song Qingsong hired a hitman
to kill Xu Meng and her father.

12:34.440 --> 12:36.240
You did it, didn't you?

12:41.200 --> 12:42.480
How did Xu Zhihong die?

12:42.560 --> 12:45.280
Where is Xu Meng? Is she dead or alive?

12:50.280 --> 12:51.400
Speak!

12:56.920 --> 12:58.960
I'll speak. Officer He,
I'll tell you everything.

12:59.040 --> 13:00.120
I'll come clean.

13:00.200 --> 13:02.400
I'll tell you everything.

13:03.360 --> 13:04.960
Song Qingsong gave me 40,000 yuan

13:05.040 --> 13:06.640
to get rid of Xu Meng and her father.

13:06.720 --> 13:08.640
He doesn't care about laws, but I do.

13:09.800 --> 13:11.440
I paid you to get rid of them,

13:11.520 --> 13:12.560
and what did you do?

13:12.640 --> 13:13.920
I asked you to do it yourself,

13:14.000 --> 13:15.400
but you paid someone else
to do it instead.

13:15.480 --> 13:17.800
That deal could have cost me my life.

13:17.880 --> 13:20.720
I wouldn't have done it,
even if he had punched me to death.

13:20.800 --> 13:21.920
What about Wolfie?

13:23.480 --> 13:25.560
You know him very well, don't you?

13:27.320 --> 13:28.680
Get rid of them.

13:33.520 --> 13:36.000
What? What wolf?

13:36.600 --> 13:38.000
I don't know him.

13:38.760 --> 13:39.600
Sure.

13:39.680 --> 13:41.640
You said it had nothing to do with you.

13:41.720 --> 13:43.000
Then tell me.

13:43.080 --> 13:44.840
How did Xu Zhihong die?

13:48.680 --> 13:51.280
Based on my understanding
of Song Qingsong,

13:51.360 --> 13:53.280
he must have hired someone else to do it.

13:53.360 --> 13:55.600
Achieve his goals at all costs.

13:55.680 --> 13:56.880
That's his personality.

13:56.960 --> 14:00.120
Why must Song Qingsong
get rid of Xu Meng and her father?

14:00.200 --> 14:01.440
I know why.

14:02.040 --> 14:02.920
Back then, Xu Meng

14:03.000 --> 14:04.840
saw the tender document
inside Song Qingsong's briefcase

14:04.920 --> 14:05.840
in the foot massage parlor.

14:05.920 --> 14:08.600
Then, she wrote to Song Qingsong
to extort money.

14:08.680 --> 14:10.280
Song Qingsong was furious

14:10.360 --> 14:11.920
and wanted her gone.

14:12.000 --> 14:14.040
Getting rid of her father
was just an afterthought.

14:14.120 --> 14:15.920
Why didn't you tell us back then?

14:17.040 --> 14:19.080
Because he was my brother-in-law.

14:19.160 --> 14:20.560
But now, it's different.

14:20.640 --> 14:22.680
Just ask me whatever you want to know.

14:22.760 --> 14:24.440
I'll tell you everything I know.

14:36.480 --> 14:37.480
Wu Shanlong.

14:37.560 --> 14:41.320
Have you contacted
Song Qingsong in recent years?

14:43.800 --> 14:45.840
We lost contact five years ago.

14:45.920 --> 14:48.760
I don't know where he's hiding now.

14:51.920 --> 14:52.960
Sir,

14:53.480 --> 14:55.280
if he contacts me,

14:56.520 --> 14:59.840
I promise to contact
the police right away.

15:43.600 --> 15:46.360
Wu Shanlong. Do not leave Weiyang.

15:46.440 --> 15:47.880
We will talk to you anytime.

15:49.600 --> 15:51.760
Sure, sir. I won't leave.

15:53.080 --> 15:54.720
Drop by when you're free.

16:06.200 --> 16:09.920
HONGYUN HUIHUANG CLUB

16:22.240 --> 16:24.160
That liar.

16:24.760 --> 16:26.160
Not a word of truth from his mouth.

16:26.240 --> 16:28.120
I made sure to ask him about Wolfie,

16:28.200 --> 16:29.800
and his eyes looked to the right.

16:31.520 --> 16:33.400
He knows that we don't have evidence,

16:34.000 --> 16:34.960
and we can't do anything about him.

16:38.240 --> 16:40.440
Now that the lead
on Song Qingsong is stuck,

16:40.520 --> 16:43.240
we can only find
another breakthrough in the scene.

16:47.120 --> 16:48.200
He.

16:48.280 --> 16:50.720
I want to go through
the suspicious residents

16:50.800 --> 16:51.640
in Yuanlongli again.

16:52.920 --> 16:54.400
You still want to head to Yuanlongli?

16:55.280 --> 16:56.800
What if you're stuck in there?

17:02.320 --> 17:03.160
He.

17:03.680 --> 17:05.280
Have you heard
of the Eye of the Vortex Theory?

17:06.000 --> 17:06.839
What?

17:06.920 --> 17:09.920
The eye of the vortex
is the center of the vortex.

17:10.000 --> 17:11.200
To see it,

17:11.280 --> 17:13.240
you must venture into the vortex.

17:13.880 --> 17:15.599
New York Block
is at the center of the crime,

17:15.680 --> 17:16.800
the eye of the vortex.

17:16.880 --> 17:18.880
Residents might come and go,

17:18.960 --> 17:21.440
but as long as the building's there,
we will find useful leads.

17:29.040 --> 17:30.040
What?

17:30.120 --> 17:31.960
You almost had it there.

17:32.040 --> 17:33.840
I thought you had lost your mind.

17:41.320 --> 17:43.320
LIANG JUAN

17:43.920 --> 17:44.760
Yes, Officer Liang?

17:48.440 --> 17:49.440
Okay. Got it.

17:50.040 --> 17:50.920
What's wrong?

17:51.000 --> 17:53.000
The Forensic Department
said they found toxins

17:53.080 --> 17:54.360
in Xu Zhihong's skull.

17:54.440 --> 17:56.080
-What kind of toxin?
-They are analyzing it.

17:57.440 --> 18:00.040
Let's do it this way.
We'll split up and search.

18:00.120 --> 18:01.400
You'll head to Yuanlongli.

18:01.480 --> 18:03.560
I'll head to the station
to ask Liang for more information.

18:03.640 --> 18:04.520
Okay.

18:07.120 --> 18:08.160
Oh.

18:08.240 --> 18:10.120
If you're taking the same route,

18:10.200 --> 18:11.960
can you pick Xiaohe up for me at school?

18:12.560 --> 18:13.960
I've been busy lately.

18:14.040 --> 18:16.760
I haven't seen her in a week.

18:21.200 --> 18:23.320
Are you and your wife…

18:26.640 --> 18:28.240
Don't be nosy. Just do your work.

18:44.480 --> 18:47.600
I'LL PICK XIAOHE UP TODAY

18:47.680 --> 18:48.800
SEND MESSAGE

18:52.520 --> 18:53.400
DATE, TIME, VIEW OPTIONS

18:53.480 --> 18:54.800
RECIPIENT: YUN

18:54.880 --> 18:56.160
I BOUGHT FISH TODAY

18:56.240 --> 18:58.520
WILL YOU BE HOME FOR DINNER TODAY?

18:58.600 --> 18:59.440
DATE, TIME, VIEW OPTIONS

18:59.520 --> 19:00.680
RECIPIENT: YUN

19:00.760 --> 19:03.200
TOMORROW IS THE PARENT-TEACHER DAY

19:03.280 --> 19:04.880
WHO'S GOING? YOU OR ME?

19:41.120 --> 19:43.920
WEIYANG NO. 1 MIDDLE SCHOOL

20:00.360 --> 20:01.800
I like your palm.

20:02.960 --> 20:05.000
Show me your right palm.

20:06.720 --> 20:07.800
Xiaohe.

20:08.680 --> 20:09.600
Uncle Ran.

20:10.240 --> 20:11.800
My uncle came to pick me up.
I have to go now. Bye!

20:14.000 --> 20:15.880
-Uncle Ran.
-Long time no see.

20:16.560 --> 20:17.840
Are you here for a case?

20:18.880 --> 20:20.440
Your dad asked me to pick you up.

20:22.120 --> 20:23.200
Oh.

20:23.280 --> 20:24.680
He finally remembers he has a daughter.

20:27.080 --> 20:28.920
Come on. He has a business trip this week.

20:33.160 --> 20:35.760
You have changed your style.

20:37.200 --> 20:38.800
People change.

20:38.880 --> 20:41.680
I was too childish.
It's not too late to grow up now.

21:03.600 --> 21:05.320
Put your legs down. It's dangerous.

21:11.360 --> 21:13.160
Tomorrow, June 8th,

21:13.240 --> 21:14.840
our national team in Group C

21:14.920 --> 21:16.680
will face the strongest opponent
in the group,

21:16.760 --> 21:17.840
the Brazil team,

21:17.920 --> 21:19.880
who is highly anticipated
to win the World Cup.

21:19.960 --> 21:24.680
Let's hope that at 7:30 p.m. tomorrow,
our national team can create a miracle.

21:24.760 --> 21:26.000
There's only one way to find out.

21:26.080 --> 21:27.000
Passion

21:27.080 --> 21:30.880
Fighting for the glory of the team

21:30.960 --> 21:32.480
Come on, come on

21:33.680 --> 21:34.880
Power

21:34.960 --> 21:38.960
We will never bow under the sky

21:39.560 --> 21:40.880
Raise your hand

21:40.960 --> 21:42.560
Passion

21:42.640 --> 21:47.040
Fighting for the glory of the team

21:47.560 --> 21:48.880
Raise your hand

21:48.960 --> 21:50.320
Power

22:00.800 --> 22:02.280
This is not the way back to my home.

22:02.920 --> 22:04.520
Are you trying to kidnap me?

22:05.920 --> 22:07.040
Don't worry.

22:07.120 --> 22:08.720
No one wants to kidnap

22:08.800 --> 22:11.240
a wild brat like you unless
there's something wrong with their brain.

22:20.480 --> 22:21.360
Why did you stop singing?

22:22.200 --> 22:23.960
Oh, no. It's Friday today.

22:24.040 --> 22:26.240
Uncle Ran, can you drive me
to the band's rehearsal?

22:26.320 --> 22:28.080
They are waiting for me.

22:28.160 --> 22:31.920
No. I promised He to take you home.

22:32.000 --> 22:33.280
After that, I have a case to investigate.

22:36.120 --> 22:37.760
Are you going to Yuanlongli?

22:40.440 --> 22:41.480
It's on the way.

22:56.480 --> 22:59.240
Liang. What did you find in his skull?

23:00.080 --> 23:03.240
We found excessive arsenic
in Xu Zhihong's skull.

23:04.200 --> 23:06.200
He was fed poison
for a long time before he died.

23:06.280 --> 23:08.240
It might be trisenox.

23:09.480 --> 23:10.880
Trisenox?

23:10.960 --> 23:12.080
Arsenic, basically.

23:12.160 --> 23:13.840
CONCLUSION: EXCESSIVE ARSENIC
FOUND IN THE VICTIM'S SKULL

23:29.360 --> 23:31.480
Xiaohe. Slow down. Wait for me.

23:31.560 --> 23:33.560
UNDERGROUND CAR PARK

23:38.000 --> 23:38.840
Uncle Ran.

23:38.920 --> 23:42.440
Are you investigating the skull?

23:43.480 --> 23:44.600
How did you know?

23:45.320 --> 23:46.880
Everyone in the underground scene knows.

23:46.960 --> 23:49.120
I knew you were involved in this case.

23:50.280 --> 23:52.320
You guys rehearse down here?

23:53.040 --> 23:55.160
Yes. What's so shocking about that?

23:55.240 --> 23:57.800
Many Western bands began in the garage.

23:59.120 --> 24:01.480
What role do you play in your band?

24:02.440 --> 24:04.360
Lead vocal and bassist.

24:05.400 --> 24:06.360
Oh.

24:06.440 --> 24:08.280
I also write songs. I just wrote one.

24:09.640 --> 24:10.920
Uncle Ran, quick.

24:12.160 --> 24:14.600
The acoustics in this spot are good.
Our keyboardist found it.

24:15.520 --> 24:16.920
Guys, I'm here.

24:17.000 --> 24:18.360
DO NOT THROW ANYTHING INSIDE
DO NOT TRESPASS

24:36.400 --> 24:38.200
Uncle Ran. Just investigate your case.

24:38.280 --> 24:39.200
I'll head back once the rehearsal is over.

24:40.480 --> 24:42.200
I'll pick you up after two hours.

24:45.480 --> 24:46.320
Hi, Officer Ran.

24:46.920 --> 24:47.760
You're…

24:48.400 --> 24:49.680
The keyboardist I told you about.

24:50.480 --> 24:52.920
You don't recognize me? I live upstairs.

24:53.000 --> 24:55.360
You chased after me back then.

24:57.440 --> 24:59.560
Little boy, your wounds are…

24:59.640 --> 25:01.320
I fell when he chased after me.

25:03.480 --> 25:04.640
Oh, it's you.

25:05.400 --> 25:07.320
He might look fragile,

25:07.400 --> 25:09.720
but he can man up if need be.

25:09.800 --> 25:12.640
He risked his life

25:12.720 --> 25:15.000
and took these instruments
out of his dad's bar.

25:15.080 --> 25:16.720
They call me the instrument sponsor.

25:18.160 --> 25:19.040
GENERAL WARD

25:19.120 --> 25:19.960
Ms. Wang.

25:20.960 --> 25:22.200
Officer He.

25:22.280 --> 25:23.560
Did Han Zi'ang say anything?

25:30.520 --> 25:32.080
He woke up just now.

25:32.160 --> 25:35.560
But no matter what the doctor or I said,

25:36.480 --> 25:38.320
he wouldn't react to us.

25:38.400 --> 25:41.800
The doctor said he had…

25:41.880 --> 25:43.120
Post-traumatic stress disorder?

25:43.720 --> 25:44.880
Yes.

25:45.560 --> 25:47.880
Madam Wang. Calm down now.

25:47.960 --> 25:50.200
Han Zi'ang encountered a traumatic event.

25:50.280 --> 25:52.160
His mind and his body
need time to recover.

25:53.200 --> 25:55.160
We're running out of time, Officer He.

25:55.240 --> 25:57.120
The school called me.

25:57.200 --> 25:59.840
They will release
his expulsion notice tomorrow.

26:00.440 --> 26:02.120
-Officer He. I'm begging you.
-Please.

26:02.200 --> 26:04.520
Get up now. I'll call the principal now.

26:15.520 --> 26:18.080
Yesterday, several parents
escalated the issue to the board meeting.

26:18.160 --> 26:20.080
The school is under immense pressure.

26:20.160 --> 26:22.760
Besides, the police didn't make
any meaningful progress.

26:22.840 --> 26:25.160
Principal Qin, I understand
the difficulty of your position.

26:25.240 --> 26:26.160
Han Zi'ang just woke up now.

26:26.840 --> 26:28.360
I will uncover the truth
as soon as possible.

26:28.440 --> 26:30.680
Then, the criminal department
will release a statement.

26:31.280 --> 26:32.960
Officer He, can you give me a deadline?

26:33.040 --> 26:33.920
Not too long.

26:34.000 --> 26:36.440
I need to justify myself
before the board and the parents.

26:36.960 --> 26:38.800
Seven days. Just seven days.

27:00.880 --> 27:02.440
Mister. Hello.

27:02.520 --> 27:03.960
Have you seen the child in this photo?

27:04.040 --> 27:05.240
No.

27:07.120 --> 27:08.040
Hi, mister.

27:08.120 --> 27:09.760
Have you seen the child in this photo?

27:09.840 --> 27:10.760
Not at all.

27:10.840 --> 27:12.000
Hi.

27:12.080 --> 27:13.640
Have you seen this child?

27:13.720 --> 27:14.560
No.

27:14.640 --> 27:16.600
Hi. Have you seen this child?

27:16.680 --> 27:17.520
No.

27:22.600 --> 27:23.760
Mr. He.

27:28.320 --> 27:29.440
Qiao.

27:29.520 --> 27:30.440
What are you doing here?

27:31.120 --> 27:32.400
I'm here to see a doctor.

27:32.480 --> 27:34.640
How do you feel now?

27:37.800 --> 27:40.000
You introduced the doctor to Xiaohe?

27:40.080 --> 27:42.080
She could've told me earlier.

27:44.800 --> 27:46.040
Wait.

27:46.120 --> 27:48.840
You're still so young.
What are you doing here?

27:48.920 --> 27:51.160
I'm working for the Redevelopment Bureau,

27:51.240 --> 27:53.440
and I have to talk to residents
who refuse to move.

27:53.520 --> 27:55.040
It's stressful.

27:55.120 --> 27:56.480
I have no one to talk to,

27:56.560 --> 27:58.920
so I come here to talk to my therapist.

27:59.000 --> 28:03.200
Have you not found a partner
after all these years?

28:04.760 --> 28:05.920
I'm not in a rush.

28:07.400 --> 28:09.400
Having a partner is nice,

28:09.480 --> 28:12.240
but I can't find anyone as sweet

28:14.280 --> 28:16.240
as Ran anymore.

28:19.560 --> 28:20.400
Qiao.

28:21.960 --> 28:24.360
We can't just live in the past.

28:25.400 --> 28:27.040
We have to move on.

28:37.840 --> 28:40.160
Officer Ran. Sorry for the long wait.

28:41.120 --> 28:42.160
I have the name list

28:42.240 --> 28:43.800
of all residents who lived
in New York Block in 1997.

28:43.880 --> 28:45.480
-Take a look.
-Thank you so much, Ma Qiang.

28:45.560 --> 28:48.240
Don't mention it.
Let me know if you need help.

28:52.160 --> 28:53.800
1997 YUANLONGLI HOUSEOWNERS
TENANTS REGISTRATION FORM

29:13.280 --> 29:14.320
Officer Ran.

29:39.600 --> 29:40.960
After I entered through the gate,

29:41.040 --> 29:43.560
I saw a familiar silhouette
and thought it was you.

29:43.640 --> 29:44.640
Turns out I am right.

29:46.960 --> 29:47.920
It's been so long.

29:48.840 --> 29:50.520
How have you been?

29:51.040 --> 29:52.240
Yes.

29:52.320 --> 29:55.560
All of us have been busy in recent years.

29:55.640 --> 29:57.920
I enrolled in the adult classes
of Weiyang University,

29:58.000 --> 29:59.320
and I graduated last year.

30:00.720 --> 30:02.880
What are you working as right now?

30:02.960 --> 30:06.080
I am now interning
in an insurance company.

30:10.320 --> 30:12.280
You encouraged me

30:12.360 --> 30:14.960
to be more confident
and to make more friends.

30:16.080 --> 30:18.080
And I did make more friends

30:18.160 --> 30:20.480
and met my neighbors.

30:20.560 --> 30:23.920
The rumors about me have stopped.

30:27.240 --> 30:28.360
That's great.

30:30.480 --> 30:31.320
Thank you.

30:34.760 --> 30:36.240
You… You're injured.

30:36.960 --> 30:38.160
You didn't even treat your injuries.

30:39.280 --> 30:40.560
Just some cuts. It's nothing.

30:40.640 --> 30:41.680
That's no good.

30:52.120 --> 30:53.520
CASUAL SNEAKERS

30:54.360 --> 30:56.200
You're being reckless.

30:56.280 --> 30:58.080
Wounds are no joking matter.

31:08.360 --> 31:09.200
Come.

31:52.960 --> 31:53.880
Do you remember?

31:53.960 --> 31:55.800
When we first met,

31:55.880 --> 31:58.080
it was you who treated my wounds.

31:58.680 --> 31:59.520
Yes.

32:00.680 --> 32:02.520
I was quite clumsy back then.

32:02.600 --> 32:04.840
Unlike you.

32:07.000 --> 32:08.280
Actually,

32:08.360 --> 32:11.280
my first job was a carer.

32:12.000 --> 32:13.440
I worked in this apartment.

32:13.520 --> 32:15.400
Ma Qiang told me before.

32:15.480 --> 32:18.760
You cared for an old man.

32:20.920 --> 32:21.760
Yes.

32:24.960 --> 32:26.120
Oh.

32:26.880 --> 32:30.800
Why did you come to Weiyang
from Guangxi? For work?

32:32.880 --> 32:36.760
When I was little, my parents split up.

32:37.480 --> 32:39.440
My dad moved abroad with my sister,

32:39.520 --> 32:42.720
and I lived with my mom in Guangxi.

32:42.800 --> 32:45.880
But after a few years,

32:47.440 --> 32:51.280
my mom passed away due to an illness.

32:53.720 --> 32:56.840
I had learned some nursing skills
in my night school,

32:57.440 --> 33:00.080
so I asked my relatives to get me a job.

33:00.160 --> 33:01.920
That was how I came to Yuanlongli.

33:02.520 --> 33:05.560
When the old man
passed away due to an accident,

33:06.160 --> 33:07.840
I had nowhere else to go.

33:07.920 --> 33:09.800
So, I continued to rent this place.

33:13.640 --> 33:16.480
It must have been tough on you
surviving on your own.

33:17.640 --> 33:20.080
But no need to carry everything
on your shoulders.

33:20.160 --> 33:21.520
If you need help,

33:22.960 --> 33:24.440
just come to me.

33:26.680 --> 33:27.960
Don't worry.

33:28.040 --> 33:30.240
The toughest part has already passed.

33:31.440 --> 33:33.280
I'm seeing the silver lining now.

33:37.800 --> 33:39.080
But…

33:42.440 --> 33:43.360
Yes?

33:43.440 --> 33:46.000
DAJIANCHANG NEIGHBORHOOD

35:44.200 --> 35:46.160
After the incident on the rooftop,

35:46.240 --> 35:49.760
I always feel that someone
is staring at me at midnight.

35:50.360 --> 35:51.720
It's creepy.

36:08.720 --> 36:10.680
Qiao. If you run into trouble,

36:10.760 --> 36:11.960
just call me.

36:15.120 --> 36:16.800
Thank you, Officer Ran.

36:16.880 --> 36:18.120
You're welcome.

36:20.840 --> 36:21.880
Give me a moment.

36:23.480 --> 36:24.520
Qing.

36:29.480 --> 36:31.920
Qing. A thief broke in again.

36:32.000 --> 36:32.960
What about your place?

36:33.040 --> 36:35.480
-Exactly. Did you lose anything?
-That guy again?

36:35.560 --> 36:36.840
Yes.

36:38.000 --> 36:39.400
What's wrong?

36:42.720 --> 36:44.560
Oh, your hidden boyfriend.

36:44.640 --> 36:46.080
Why didn't you tell us?

36:46.160 --> 36:47.800
No. Don't say that.

36:47.880 --> 36:51.120
This is Ran Fangxu. Officer Ran.
He's here to investigate.

36:52.320 --> 36:55.320
Mr. Officer, there's a pervert
in this building.

36:55.960 --> 36:56.880
We live in Unit 1713.

36:56.960 --> 36:58.640
Our clothes that we hung to dry

36:58.720 --> 37:00.480
and our shoes were all stolen by a thief.

37:00.560 --> 37:03.120
I reported it to the management,
but Qian Dajun doesn't care at all.

37:03.200 --> 37:05.600
Also, that pervert also stole lingerie.

37:05.680 --> 37:07.240
-Disgusting!
-That's right.

37:07.320 --> 37:09.280
Mr. Officer, you must intervene.

37:10.520 --> 37:12.520
Don't worry.
I'll investigate this properly.

37:12.600 --> 37:14.320
No need to investigate.

37:14.400 --> 37:16.920
We all know who the pervert is.

37:17.000 --> 37:18.240
-Yes. We know.
-That's right.

37:41.720 --> 37:42.640
Speak.

37:43.240 --> 37:44.720
Why do you stare at the unit
belonging to the Xus?

37:45.360 --> 37:47.520
I… No, I didn't do that.

37:47.600 --> 37:48.760
I didn't do that.

37:48.840 --> 37:49.880
You didn't?

37:50.640 --> 37:52.000
Let's speak at the police station then.

37:52.080 --> 37:52.920
Come.

37:54.520 --> 37:56.120
I'll come clean.

37:56.200 --> 37:58.040
I did do it.

38:03.480 --> 38:07.120
Someone paid me to do it.

38:07.200 --> 38:09.680
In the summer of 1996,

38:09.760 --> 38:13.800
someone paid me 500 yuan
to spy on the unit opposite.

38:13.880 --> 38:16.360
He told me to call him

38:16.440 --> 38:18.560
if I found anything unusual.

38:18.640 --> 38:21.160
You've been spying on them
for six years just for 500 yuan?

38:22.360 --> 38:25.120
A work accident left me handicapped.

38:25.200 --> 38:26.560
And I'm divorced.

38:26.640 --> 38:29.720
I live all alone in this apartment.

38:29.800 --> 38:32.080
I need something to entertain myself.

38:32.160 --> 38:33.320
Speak.

38:34.520 --> 38:35.680
Who hired you?

38:35.760 --> 38:37.760
What's his name? What does he look like?

38:38.520 --> 38:39.400
It was a man.

38:39.480 --> 38:41.920
I don't know his name.

38:42.000 --> 38:44.440
He looked like he was around 25 years old.

38:44.520 --> 38:46.960
He was tall and bespectacled.

38:47.040 --> 38:49.760
He had a 30/70 side part,
and he looked like a gentleman.

39:31.960 --> 39:33.680
What a jerk.

39:33.760 --> 39:36.080
I won't forgive you.
